name: MOONSHARD DAGGER
description: This dagger was made from shards of the Moon's soul and given to the strongest warrior of her people for protection. Moon, without the missing pieces of her soul, became the watcher of her people.  In time, people stopped believing in the Moon because they could no longer feel it near them. Legend has it that if all the missing pieces of her soul are collected, Moon will return to her people and a new era will begin.
